Union MaybeI32 has none; some value: i32.

To make maybe from owned, giving MaybeI32.
Let cells be owned buffer of 1 i32 filled with 7.
Give MaybeI32.some with value be cells at 0.

To main, giving i32.
Let maybe be make maybe from owned.
Give match maybe:
MaybeI32.some with value gives value;
otherwise gives 0.
